headline: GTA Online Update
subtitle: Introducing the new Dewbauchee Massacro
content:
Sophisticated, superior, class-obsessed and with more than a little aggression under the hood, this grand tourer from Dewbauchee is a British built classic, which means it is now designed, built and owned overseas.

The Massacro is featured in the new High Life race ‘Stock Market Crash’ and is available to purchase now from legendarymotorsport.net.
